msContents.summary: Supercommentary on İbrāhīm Gülşenī's commentary of Rūmī's Mas̲navī-i maʻnavī.

name.#text: Turkish Manuscripts Collection (Burke Library at Union Theological Seminary)

persName.#text: Sunbulī, Muḥammad Darvīsh Nūr al-Dīn, active 1862

supportDesc.extent: 82 foliated leaves : 211 x 154 (163 x 100) mm, bound to 212 x 161 x 14 mm

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in ruqʻah in black ink; pointed.

binding.p: Textured green paper over cardboard (type III); plain paper doublure.

origin.p: Copy completed in 1270 A.H. (1853 or 1854 CE) (f. 82v).

provenance: Formerly owned by Darvīsh Nūr al-Dīn (stamps, f. 1r-2r).
Given as a waqf (pious donation) by al-Sayyid Darvīsh Muḥammad Nūr al-Dīn Sunbulī in 1279 A.H. (1862 or 1863 CE)  (note ink, f. 1r).

term: İbrahim bin Muhammed Gülşenî,---1534--Şerh-i maʻnevi-i şerif
